A summer recap so far. Living our best summer lives with swimming, bike rides, hitting local spots, bowling, zoo/ aquarium visits, crafting, reading, movie watching, s’more/ice cream eating and hanging out with friends! @the.austin.diaries

Happy summer friends! Back with a recap of our San Diego trip. It was nearly impossible to fit all this goodness in one reel. We explored museums, little Italy,  SD zoo, Legoland, the NAT, balboa park, & Coronado beach. We ate so many things.. lasagna, pizza, apple fries, shake shack, but the gelato and ramen were our favorites oh and the Legoland roasted corn! Hahah on to he next city… and I better get a mini album going…
Saved some memorabilia from our trip and I’m gathering supplies so I can create a quick 4” mini before I forget all about it. Do you save allllll the things from trips?

Hello! I’m here to share the start of our San Diego album. We have two small road trips planned before school and work start up for us. Ugh. Summer went by so fast! #scrapbooking #minialbum #travelersnotebook #storyteller #photohoarder #summerscrapbook

I believe we crammed in a whole lot more than I remember ha! Here’s some pages of our tour of little Italy! The lasagna was so delicious but our fav was the gelato!
